---
By: Eliphas Levi
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 475
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Truth
---
Everything that is true is beautiful. The only vanity under the sun is error
and falsehood. Even pain and death are beautiful because they are the
work which purifies and the transfiguration which delivers.
